channel.title: Port Checkers Saying Two Different things?
channel.description: I am completely baffled at what is happening. I have port forwarded my router just as a tutorial instructed and set up a static Ip just as instructed. The PF Portchecker tells me that 43594 TCP and UDP ports are open on my computer, but the problem is, canyouseeme portchecker Keeps saying Connection Refused. What is happening? How can two port checkers say two different things?
